Kelli R. KiemleAIF®Director of Marketing and Client Experiencekkiemle@hhga.com



Kelli holds multiple roles with Halbert Hargrove. As Director of Marketing and Client Experience, she sets the tone for the quality and character of Halbert Hargrove’s client service relationships. She helped establish Halbert Hargrove’s current intern program, and manages several client service managers as well as interns. Kelli is also responsible for overseeing the firm’s wide-ranging marketing and communications initiatives.
