About Halbert Hargrove

WE BELIEVE IN
BUILDING GREAT
RELATIONSHIPS



We are an employee-owned firm that has strategically grown from a trusted family business. Over the decades, we’ve steadily fought to defend our clients’ legacies. Today, we’re promoting a new generation of leadership. Our principles remain deeply rooted: Family, loyalty, discipline, patient capital, an entrepreneurial spirit, freedom to excel, joy in work done well—and giving back.







